# Improvements Backlog

Prioritized list of planned improvements. See [`README.md`](./README.md) for status vocabulary and workflow.

Items here are commitments to address eventually — not yet decisions about *how*. When an item is implemented, the design choices it produces are captured as ADRs in [`docs/decisions/`](../decisions/).

Newest on top.

